title: Create - Verified Gamer Role
body:
Role: Verified Gamer

Purpose: To contribute to Gamer DAO in any way you can, have fun and build relationships with other members.

Accountabilities: 

- Act and Operate in-line with Gamer DAO values, principles and rules. 

- Share the word with your friends!

- Contribute to Gamer DAO where you can.
author: 0x380C7200892581b7392CA00DA759A4072B67460D
